  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Professional Level Edits Effortlessly</h2>Intuitive editing tools that help you set objects in motion, completely transform a scene's location, and create cinematic effects.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mask & Blend</h2>Layer, shape, and blend to create artistic scenes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688030/extras/736efa264019501264088eab9c58fbfa.avif?t=1754574002\" width=472 height=296 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Green Screen</h2>Remove backgrounds and create Hollywood-style special effects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688030/extras/22bdabf0f77b70efbfc0093de1db40f9.avif?t=1754574002\" width=526 height=294 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Motion Tracking</h2>Add text and graphics that follow the motion of objects to elevate your footage.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688030/extras/037cf8a9c89d830f8fa912e956d9ac78.avif?t=1754574002\" width=526 height=294 /></span></h2></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Limitless Possibilities, Right at Your Fingertips</h2>Bring your imagination to life with our wide array of tools to help customize your projects. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customizable Titles</h2>Easily create titles with unique customization tools and animated templates.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688030/extras/41f9b0ad09773f841984f0f11b4f5639.avif?t=1754574002\" width=524 height=292 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Transitions</h2>Choose from a variety of styles to seamlessly connect your shots.</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video Effects</h2>Transform and modify the look of your video with magical effects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688030/extras/87caf3a5b45935280abce4a7dbd337ec.avif?t=1754574002\" width=526 height=294 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LUTs & Color Match</h2>Match color to quickly balance or change the aesthetic of your videos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688030/extras/0af2779af1b13cc9ab8f8c0ad5ecf040.avif?t=1754574002\" width=526 height=292 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Screen Recording</h2>Capture, edit, and share video demos and tutorials to become the next YouTube star.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688030/extras/8f01b01f9f46e486cea058008818a533.avif?t=1754574002\" width=504 height=284 /></span></h2></ul>",
